Third-party
-----------

The transformer math implemented here is prior art (Vaswani et al.
2017; Karpathy's `llama2.c`; the open `transformers` reference
implementation; published descriptions of RoPE, RMSNorm, GeGLU, SwiGLU,
GQA/MQA, Gated DeltaNet, TurboQuant, RHT, Q4_0, and Q4_K_M). The Zig
and GLSL implementation in this repo is original.

The Apache 2.0 license file applies to all source code in this
repository (`src/`, `shaders/`, `build.zig`, `build.zig.zon`, and the
`docs/` and `README.md` documentation). It does not extend to weights,
checkpoints, or third-party material that may be loaded at runtime —
those carry their own upstream licenses (e.g., Gemma's terms,
Llama's terms, Mistral's terms, Qwen's terms).
